	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=66620><span id= >Slein</span></a><br><span id=notbold>234 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.67]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>3 types of haste: permanent, spell, song; all 3 stack with eachother, none stack with others of the same type.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Ok, I'll shut up now.<br><br>Slein Jinn<br>Dread Lord on everyone's least favorite server, E'ci<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325772" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325772</a></td></tr>
